Package: l1rotation
Title: Identify Loading Vectors under Sparsity in Factor Models
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Simon", "Freyaldenhoven", , "simon.freyaldenhoven@phil.frb.org", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("Ryan", "Kobler", , "kobleary@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Simplify the loading matrix in factor models using the l1 criterion as proposed in Freyaldenhoven (2025) <https://doi.org/10.21799/frbp.wp.2020.25>. Given a data matrix, find the rotation of the loading matrix with the smallest l1-norm and/or test for the presence of local factors with with main function local_factors().
